description: The project aims to increase the capacity of central and local governments to promote, develop, operate and manage public-private partnership projects for infrastructure development and the provision of basic services.

subproject.description: The output of the project is targeted through the implementation of 5 activities: Establishing adequate Policy, Legal and Institutional Frameworks for Public Private Partnership Development at the Local Level; Building Local Capacity for Public Private Partnerships; Designing and implementing Innovative Partnership Arrangements; Support to Corporate Social Responsibility Initiatives; and Fostering multi-stakeholder partnerships in the framework of the UN Global Compact in Moldova.
